BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

[```\newcommand{\amp}{&}
\begin{aligned}
[$given]\amp=\frac{[$given]}{1}\\
\amp=\frac{[$given]}{1}\cdot\frac{[$factornumU]}{[$factordenU]}\\
\amp=\frac{[$a]\cdot [$factornumU]}{1\cdot [$factorden]}\\
\amp=[$get]
\end{aligned}
```]

END_PGML_SOLUTION

